# Taush, Ufimsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Taush (; , Tıwış) is a rural locality (a village) in Kirillovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 55 as of 2010. It has 1 street.
Geography
Taush is located 30&nbsp;km northeast of Ufa (the district's administrative centre) by road. Gribovka is the nearest rural locality.
